<div id="review_117761090" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/117761090" />
    <a title="Brittany" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/2105668-brittany"><img alt="Brittany" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1482877071p2/2105668.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/117761090?book_show_action=true">Aug 20, 2010</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Brittany" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Brittany" href="/user/show/2105668-brittany">Brittany</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780849921438" href="/book/show/6634435-when-god-whispers-your-name">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2105668-brittany?shelf=non-fiction">non-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2105668-brittany?shelf=christian">christian</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2105668-brittany?shelf=2010-reads">2010-reads</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer117761090" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7151204435241739086">This was my first Lucado book experience. I was intrigued by his Grace for the Moments devotional I am doing and picked up this book. Honestly I was sincerely disappointed! It was by no means revelatory, as what I look for in Christian non-fiction. I&apos;m going to give Max the benefit of the doubt and hope not all his books are mashed up stories. I&apos;d much rather read someones thoughts than a basic themed recollection of stories. <br/><br/>The stories weren&apos;t bad and didn&apos;t make for hard or boring reading, it</span>
  <span id="freeText7151204435241739086" style="display:none">This was my first Lucado book experience. I was intrigued by his Grace for the Moments devotional I am doing and picked up this book. Honestly I was sincerely disappointed! It was by no means revelatory, as what I look for in Christian non-fiction. I'm going to give Max the benefit of the doubt and hope not all his books are mashed up stories. I'd much rather read someones thoughts than a basic themed recollection of stories. <br /><br />The stories weren't bad and didn't make for hard or boring reading, it was just not what I expected nor hoped for. </span>
  <a data-text-id="7151204435241739086" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


