        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2387378196" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1344000825485732938">The book is easy to read and filled with enjoyable stories. However, when I got the book, I wasn’t aware the stories/chapters would be isolated stories or unrelated vignettes. And although I enjoy each story I think the title is a little misleading as I anticipated stories that provided instances or examples of “God Whispering Your Name.” What I found instead was a book about faithful advice. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


