    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer98807275" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4517947164386313214">I haven&apos;t read anything by Max Lucado in years, and I had a hard time getting into this. He has so many good things to say, and I think his teaching is solid, but his writing is a little choppy for me. I imagine he&apos;s a good speaker, because he gets to the point quickly and uses lots of illustrations. Just not my style of literature.</span>
  <span id="freeText4517947164386313214" style="display:none">I haven't read anything by Max Lucado in years, and I had a hard time getting into this. He has so many good things to say, and I think his teaching is solid, but his writing is a little choppy for me. I imagine he's a good speaker, because he gets to the point quickly and uses lots of illustrations. Just not my style of literature.</span>
