        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4032581627" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer753138679275102121">I bought this book on an audiobook app called Chirp because it was inexpensive and thought the book fit in well with the spiritual journey I have been on lately. Although it had some lulling moments in the middle, I found the beginning interesting, and by the end of the book, I was back into the message. I like the idea of having a new name when you enter heaven. It makes me ponder what mine might be. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


